text: Prince Moren of the [[Lhazaar Principalities]] is an infamous [[death knight]]. Once a bold swashbuckler and beloved prince, he betrayed his beloved and his treachery resulted in the destruction of his principality. Murdered by his own crew, he now he sails the [[Lhazaar Sea]] in a [[Ship of Bones]], hunting treacherous captains and forcing them to serve his vessel.
title: Moren
